generated_description: ibaraki mokuzaishi co., ltd. is a company based in mito, ibaraki prefecture, specializing in the logistics and distribution of wood products. the company handles a wide range of materials, including ibaraki prefecture-produced wood, domestic and imported wood, and building materials. they offer services such as pre-cut processing, delivery, and woodwork, focusing on connecting forests with homes. additionally, they provide consultation services for housing and materials, aiming to contribute to the regional economy and environmental conservation. the company also engages in non-residential woodwork for public and welfare facilities, and it serves as the office for the "ibaraki mokuzaishi - house from the forest" regional housing greenization project.
